 "overview": "\u003Cp\u003EBroadPeak Partners is the developer of K3 Server.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EK3 Server is the first point to point integration harness for large enterprises.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003ECompanies around the world spend nearly $300 Billion Dollars integrating applications.  While EAI and ESB tools have been around for over 12 years they still only account for 6% of this market.  Why?\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EThe business demands integration now and will not wait.  This is why custom point to point integration is done again and again.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EK3 Server is the world\u0026#8217;s first point to point integration harness designed to streamline development, provide total transparency, and offer operation tools to point to point integration.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EK3 Server leverages an top shelf architecture to make integration of disparate systems easy.\u003C/p\u003E",
